an%2C%26quot%3B%20Uthappa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mocking%2C%20trolling%2C%20the%20memes%20about%20his%20fitness.%20You%20don't%20think%20it%20hurts%20him%3F%20It%20hurts%20him.%20It%20hurts%20any%20human%20being.%20How%20many%20people%20actually%20know%20the%20reality%20of%20it%3F%20Hardik%20is%20dealing%20with%20mental%20health%20issues%2C%20for%20sure.%20We%2C%20as%20people%2C%20I%20understand%2C%20as%20Indians%2C%20we%20are%20emotional.%20But%20it%20is%20not%20right%20to%20impose%20this%20kind%20of%20treatment%20on%20any%20human%20being.%20It%20is%20unbecoming%20as%20a%20society%20for%20us%20to%20do%20that%20to%20someone%20and%20be%20okay%20with%20it.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20laughing%20along%20with%20it.%20We%20should%20not%20be%20forwarding%20these%20memes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUthappa%20added%20that%20the%20all-rounder%20is%20right%20in%20securing%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20our%20job%2C%20yes%20it's%20passion%20too%2C%20but%20it's%20what%20puts%20the%20food%20on%20the%20table%20for%20me.%20My%20job%20is%20on%20display%20for%20you%20to%20criticise.%20A%20corporate%20person's%20job%20is%20not%20on%20television%20to%20criticise%2C%20or%20have%20an%20opinion%20about%20either.%20When%20that%20is%20the%20case%2C%20you%20have%20to%20exercise%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20empathy%20and%20dignity%20to%20the%20other%20person%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20fail.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20beautiful%20things%20we%20did%20as%20a%20country%20is%20our%20expression%20to%20love%2C%20and%20our%20reaction%20to%20our%20Indian%20team%20after%20we%20lost%20the%20World%20Cup.%20That's%20how%20we%20should%20be%20as%20a%20society%2C%20and%20as%20Indians%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Uthappa%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713640320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fa9qsdl9_hardik-pandya-bcci_625x300_16_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fhardik-pandya-dealing-with-m