yers%2F62477-travis-michael-head-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETravis%20Head%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108562-abhishek-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shahbaz%20Ahmed%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F51351-shahbaz-ahmed-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShahbaz%20Ahmed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20SRH%20put%20up%20an%20intimidating%20total%20of%20267%2F6%20in%2020%20overs.%20However%2C%20DC%20put%20up%20a%20strong%20fight%20with%20youngster%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jake%20Fraser-McGurk%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112550-jake-fraser-mcgurk-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJake%20Fraser-McGurk%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0taking%20a%20leading%20role.%20He%20came%20out%20all%20guns%20blazing%20scoring%20a%2015-ball%20half%20century%2C%20the%20fasted%20in%20IPL%202024%20this%20season.%20It's%20the%20joint%20third-fastest%20fifty%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20tournament.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20fastest%20half-century%20by%20a%20DC%20batter%20in%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Fraser-McGurk's%20innings%20included%20seven%20sixes%20and%20five%20fours%20as%20he%20ended%20on%2065%20off%20just%2018%20balls.%20However%2C%20he%20was%20most%20brutal%20against%20SRH%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Washington%20Sundar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108593-washington-sundar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWashington%20Sundar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20third%20over%20which%20went%20for%2030%20runs.%C2%A0%C2%A0Fraser-McGurk%20hit%204%2C%204%2C%206%2C%204%2C%206%2C%206%20as%20DC%20cruised%20in%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20The%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20opening%20pair%20of%20Travis%20Head%20and%20Abhishek%20Sharma%20continued%20their%20rampage%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%2C%20posting%20the%20highest%20powerplay%20total%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20competition%20and%20rewriting%20other%20record%20books%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDC's%20return%20to%20their%20home%20arena%2C%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Stadium%2C%20was%20not%20at%20all%20sweet%20and%20was%20memorable%20for%20all%20the%20wrong%20reasons.%20Right%20from%20ball%20one%2C%20opener%20Head-Abhishek%20smashed%20fours%20and%20sixes%20left%20and%20right%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20bowler.%20After%20demolishing%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20and%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20with%20250-plus%20totals%20of%20277%20and%20287%20runs%20respectively%2C%20which%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20highest%20score%20in%20IPL%20history%2C%20the%20Aussie-Indian%20pair%20laid%20down%20foundation%20for%20yet%20another%20big%20score.%20SRH%20ended%20with%20266%2F7%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHead%20and%20Abhishek%20amassed%20125%20runs%20in%20just%20six%20overs%20of%20their%20powerplay%2C%20the%20highest-ever%20powerplay%20total%20in%20IPL%20history.%20They%20broke%20the%20record%20of%20105%2F0%20put%20up%20by%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20against%20RCB%20in%20the%20IPL%202017.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20highest%20powerplay%20score%20in%20the%20history%20of%20T20%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETravis%20ended%20the%20powerplay%20at%2084%20in%20just%2026%20balls%2C%20making%20it%20the%20highest%20powerplay%20score%20for%20SRH%20in%20the%20IPL%20by%20a%20single%20player%2C%20outdoing%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Warner%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1285-david-warner-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Warner%3C%2Fa%3E's%2062%20in%2023%20balls%20against%20KKR%20in%20Hyderabad%20back%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETravis%20reached%20his%20half-century%20in%20just%2016%20balls%2C%20tying%20with%20Abhishek%20Sharma's%2016-ball%20fifty%20against%20MI%20in%20this%20season%20for%20the%20fastest%20fifty%20in%20IPL%20history%20for%20SRH.%20Rajasthan%20Royals%20(RR)%20batter%20Abhishek%20Jaiswal%20has%20a%2013-ball%20fifty%2C%20the%20fastest%20ever%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHead%20also%20reached%20his%20fifty%20for%20the%20third%20time%20season%20within%20the%20powerplay%20itself.%20David%20Warner%20has%20repeated%20this%20feat%20six%20times%20in%20IPL%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Chris%20Gayle%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F199-chris-gayle-playerprofile%5C%22%3EChris%20Gayle%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Narine%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1456-sunil-narine-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Narine%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20done%20so%20thrice%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESRH%20reached%20the%20100-run%20mark%20in%20just%20five%20overs%20with%20a%20huge%20six%20from%20Abhishek.%20This%20is%20the%20fastest%20team%20hundred%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20outdoing%20the%20feat%20by%20the%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20reaching%20the%20100-run%20mark%20in%20just%20six%20overs%20against%20Punjab%20Kings%20(PBKS)%20in%20the%20IPL%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%2010%20overs%2C%20SRH%20was%20158%2F4.%20Despite%20the%20fact%20that%20Delhi%20spinners%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Axar%20Patel%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63024-akshar-rajeshbhai-patel-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAxar%20Patel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kuldeep%20Yadav%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F63624-kuldeep-yadav-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20made%20a%20comeback%20with%20some%20quick%20wickets%2C%20they%20could%20not%20stop%20SRH%20from%20posting%20the%20biggest%20total%20in%20IPL%20history%20after%2010%20overs%2C%20outdoing%20SRH's%20148%2F2%20against%20Mumbai%20Indians%20made%20not%20so%20long%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESRH%20reached%20their%20200-run%20mark%20in%2014.5%20overs%2C%20making%20it%20the%20third%20fastest%20instance%20of%20a%20team%20reaching%20200%20runs%20in%20the%20IPL.%20The%20fastest%20instance%20was%20by%20RCB%2C%20who%20reached%20the%20200-run%20mark%20in%2014.1%20overs%20during%20a%2015-over%20game%20against%20Punjab%20in%202016.%20The%20fastest%20instance%20of%20a%20team%20reaching%20200%20runs%20in%20an%20IPL%20game%20of%2020%20overs%20is%20also%20owned%20by%20SRH%2C%20who%20did%20so%20in%2014.4%20overs%20against%20MI%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20third%20instance%20of%20a%20250-plus%20run%20score%20by%20SRH%20in%20T20s%2C%20tying%20them%20with%20Surrey%20for%20the%20most%20250-plus%20scores%20in%20T20%20cricket.%2022%20sixes%20were%20smashed%20in%20this%20innings%2C%20making%20it%20the%20joint%20most%20sixes%20in%20an%20IPL%20innings%2C%20equaling%20SRH's%20record%20of%2022%20sixes%20against%20RCB%2C%20which%20came%20recently%20in%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20266-runs%20scored%20by%20SRH%20is%20the%20fourth-highest%20total%20in%20the%20IPL.%20The%20Orange%20Army%20owns%20the%20highest%20ever%20total%20as%20well%2C%20scoring%20287%2F3%20against%20RCB%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20six%20matches%2C%20Head%20has%20scored%20324%20runs%20at%20an%20average%20of%2054.00%2C%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20216.00.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20century%20and%20two%20fifties%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%20102.%20He%20is%20the%20second-highest%20run-getter%20in%20the%20tournament%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20end%2C%20Abhishek%20has%20scored%20257%20runs%20in%20seven%20innings%20at%20an%20average%20of%2036.71%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20215.96%2C%20with%20a%20fifty.%20His%20best%20score%20is%2063.%20He%20is%20the%2010th-highest%20run-getter%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20SRH%20was%20put%20on%20field%20first%20by%20DC.%20Head%20(89%20in%2032%20balls%2C%20with%2011%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20and%20Abhishek%20(46%20in%2012%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20six%20sixes)%20put%20on%20an%20explosive%20stand%20of%20131%20runs%20in%206.2%20overs.%20Later%2C%20contributions%20from%20Shahbaz%20Ahmed%20(59*%20in%2029%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20five%20sixes)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nitish%20Kumar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1352-nitish-kumar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENitish%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20(37%20in%2027%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20came%20in%20handy%20to%20take%20SRH%20to%20266%2F7%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuldeep%20Yadav%20was%20the%20pick%20of%20the%20bowlers%20for%20DC%20with%204%2F55.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mukesh%20Kumar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108561-mukesh-kumar-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMukesh%20Kumar%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Axar%20Patel%20also%20got%20a%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713637500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fnui7i6b8_jake-frasermcgurk_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2F4-4-6-4-6-6-jake-fraser-mcgurk-on-rampage-vs-india-star-as-he-slams-fastest-50-of-ipl-2024-5486376%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jake%20Fraser-McGurk's%20innings%20included%20seven%20sixes%20and%20five%20fours%20as%20he%20ended%20on%2065%20off%20just%2018%20balls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20US%20House%20pass%20critical%20Ukraine%20aid%20package%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713637149000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FEA1A%2Fproduction%2F_133203995_p0hs3lql.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68866766%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20long-awaited%20vote%20comes%20as%20Kyiv%20faces%20a%20weapons%20shortage%20in%20its%20fig