EThe%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20perform%20better%20this%20time%20than%20what%20it%20achieved%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20top%20economist%20and%20psephologist%20told%20NDTV%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurjit%20Bhalla%2C%20whose%20new%20book%20'How%20We%20Vote'%20details%20the%20voter's%20mindset%2C%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20said%20the%20BJP%20may%20get%20330%20to%20350%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20statistical%20possibility%2C%20they%20should%20get%20330%20to%20350%20seats%20on%20their%20own.%20This%20is%20just%20the%20BJP%2C%20not%20including%20its%20alliance%20partners%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said%2C%20agreeing%20that%20the%20party%20whose%20campaign%20is%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20would%20likely%20see%20a%205%20to%207%20per%20cent%20rise%20in%20seats%20won%20compared%20to%20the%202019%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20a%20wave%20election.%20Every%20election%20has%20a%20potential%20(to%20be%20a%20wave).%20But%20it%20may%20not%20also%20be%20a%20wave%20election%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20economist%20who%20has%20tracked%20elections%20in%20India%20for%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Opposition%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said%20the%20party%20may%20get%2044%20seats%2C%20or%202%20per%20cent%20less%20than%20what%20it%20won%20in%20the%202014%20election%2C%20the%20year%20PM%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20the%20(Opposition)%20alliance%20is%20the%20leadership.%20The%20economy%20matters%20the%20most%2C%20the%20leadership%20matters%20second.%20And%20both%20of%20them%20are%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP.%20If%20the%20Opposition%20had%20selected%20a%20leader%20who%20could%20have%20a%20mass%20appeal%20or%20approximating%20half%20the%20appeal%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%2C%20then%20I%20think%20it%20could%20be%20a%20contest%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20predicted%20the%20BJP%20would%20likely%20win%20at%20least%20five%20seats%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20traditionally%20a%20weak%20party.%20%26quot%3BI%20won't%20be%20surprised%20if%2C%20of%20all%20the%20places%2C%20the%20BJP%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20gain%20over%20five%20seats.%20In%20Kerala%2C%20maybe%20one%20or%20two%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20attributed%20this%20possibility%20to%20the%20improvement%20in%20people's%20living%20conditions.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20votes%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20how%20much%20improvement%20has%20been%20in%20people's%20lives.%20That's%20the%20basic%20premise.%20It's%20not%20caste%2C%20not%20gender%2C%20not%20the%20various%20factors%20that%20people%20attribute%20to%2C%20but%20it%20is%20precisely%20what%20Bill%20Clinton%20had%20said%20in%201992%2C%20'It's%20the%20economy%2C%20stupid'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20say%20is%20that%20because%20of%20the%20significant%20improvement%20in%20their%20lives%2C%201%20per%20cent%20or%2014%20million%20are%20poor%20by%20the%20old%20definition%20of%20poverty.%20Look%2C%20we%20have%20developed%2C%20per%20capita%20consumption%20has%20improved%2C%20lives%20have%20improved%2C%20so%20raise%20the%20poverty%20line.%20In%20some%20sense%2C%20maybe%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20population%20is%20poor.%20Poverty%20is%20relative%20now%2C%20no%20longer%20absolute%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20economist%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20poor%20will%20always%20be%20with%20us.%20The%20rich%20will%20always%20be%20with%20us.%20It%20depends%20on%20how%20you%20define%20who%20are%20the%20poor%2C%20and%20we%20use%20the%20World%20Bank%20definition%20of%20%241.9%20per%20person%20per%20day.%20We%20are%20saying%20it%20should%20be%20doubled%20because%20of%20the%20improvement%20in%20lives%20and%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20dismissed%20data%20by%20the%20think%20tank%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%20as%20unreliable%2C%20and%20faulted%20the%20Opposition%20of%20selectively%20using%20the%20CMIE%20data%20to%20target%20the%20BJP%20during%20election%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverywhere%20in%20the%20world%2C%20the%20Opposition%20will%20always%20say%20inflation%20is%20high%2C%20there%20are%20too%20few%20jobs.%20But%20there%20are%20less%20percentage%20of%20people%20unemployed%20than%20in%202019%20in%20India%2C%20for%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAm%20not%20the%20only%20one%20to%20question%20the%20(CMIE)%20data.%20Several%20authors%20have.%20THey%20are%20saying%20less%20women%20in%20India%20are%20in%20the%20workforce%20today%20than%20in%20Yemen%20and%20Iraq%2C%20less%20than%2010%20per%20cent%3F%20This%20is%20the%20point%20I%20want%20to%20make.%20It%20is%20so%20absurd.%20Why%20has%20it%20got%20currency%3F%20Because%20the%20Opposition%20loves%20it.%20The%20CMIE%20data%20I%20think%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20untrustworthy%20data%20published%20anywhere%20at%20any%20time%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bhalla%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2026.%20The%20rest%20will%20be%20held%20in%20May.%20Votes%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20June%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713636120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5mgk8n38_surjit-bhalla_625x300_20_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-bjp-may-get-350-seats-on-its-own-5-in-tamil-nadu-top-economist-surjit-bhalla-to-ndtv-5486663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20likely%20to%20perform%20better%20this%20time%20than%20what%20it%20achieved%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20a%20top%20economist%20and%20psephologist%20told%20NDTV%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww