0a%20major%20new%20weapons%20package%20for%20Ukraine%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Republicans%2C%20influenced%20by%20the%20party's%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20are%20reluctant%20to%20provide%20funding%20to%20Kyiv%20for%20the%20drawn-out%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20financing%20of%20the%20war%20has%20become%20a%20point%20of%20contention%20ahead%20of%20a%20presidential%20election%20in%20November%20that%20is%20expected%20to%20pit%20Biden%20against%20Trump%20once%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohnson%2C%20after%20months%20of%20hesitation%2C%20finally%20threw%20his%20support%20behind%20a%20%2461%20billion%20package%20for%20Ukraine%20that%20includes%20economic%20assistance%20and%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20also%20allows%20Biden%20to%20confiscate%20and%20sell%20Russian%20assets%20and%20provide%20the%20money%20to%20Ukraine%20to%20finance%20reconstruction%2C%20a%20move%20that%20has%20been%20embraced%20by%20other%20G7%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20put%20it%20bluntly%2C%20I'd%20rather%20send%20bullets%20to%20Ukraine%20than%20American%20boys%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20bill%20passes%20the%20House%2C%20the%20upper%20chamber%20could%20take%20it%20on%20as%20early%20as%20Tuesday%2C%20Senate%20Democratic%20leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20%2413%20billion%20in%20military%20assistance%20has%20been%20allocated%20for%20America's%20historic%20ally%20Israel%20in%20its%20war%20against%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20will%20essentially%20be%20used%20to%20reinforce%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%20air%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20%249%20billion%20will%20be%20earmarked%20to%20address%20%26quot%3Bthe%20dire%20need%20for%20humanitarian%20assistance%20for%20Gaza%20as%20well%20as%20other%20vulnerable%20populations%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20legislation%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20i