lapse%2Farticleshow%2F109464112.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthird-temporary-channel-opens-for-vessels-to-baltimore-port-after-bridge-collapse%2Famp_articleshow%2F109464112.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fthird-temporary-channel-opens-for-vessels-to-baltimore-port-after-bridge-collapse%2Famp_articleshow%2F109464112.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray%20On%20Devendra%20Fadnavis'%202019%20Promise%20Involving%20Son%20Aaditya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20Saturday%20claimed%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20had%20told%20him%20in%202019%20that%20he%20would%20groom%20his%20son%20Aaditya%20Thackeray%20as%20the%20next%20CM%20of%20Maharashtra%20as%20part%20of%20the%20power-sharing%20agreement%20between%20the%20two%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20also%20said%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%2C%20had%20told%20him%20that%20he%20would%20move%20to%20the%20Centre%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20rally%20in%20Dharavi%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20claimed%20the%20then%20BJP%20chief%20Amit%20Shah%20had%20come%20to%20Matoshree%2C%20the%20private%20residence%20of%20the%20Thackerays%2C%20to%20seek%20an%20alliance%20with%20Shiv%20Sena%20(undivided).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20Fadnavis%20was%20made%20to%20sit%20outside%20the%20room%20of%20late%20Bal%20Thackeray%20while%20the%20two%20leaders%20(Shah%20and%20Thackeray)%20discussed%20modalities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20assured%20to%20me%20that%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister%20will%20be%20shared%20for%202.5%20years%20(between%20BJP%20and%20Sena-undivided)%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLater%2C%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20told%20me%2C%20Uddhav%20Ji%2C%20I%20will%20groom%20Aaditya%20for%202.5%20years.%20We%20can%20make%20him%20CM%20after%202.5%20years.%20I%20told%20him%20(Fadnavis)%20that%20he%20(Aaditya)%20is%20just%20starting%20his%20electoral%20career.%20Do%20not%20put%20anything%20like%20this%20in%20his%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20how%20a%20senior%20leader%20like%20him%20would%20work%20under%20Aaditya%2C%20he%20(Fadnavis)%20said%20he%20would%20move%20to%20Delhi%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray's%20claim%20evoked%20a%20sharp%20reaction%20from%20Mr%20Fadnavis%2C%20current%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20in%20the%20Mahayuti%20government%20of%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20NCP%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20said%20Mr%20Thackeray%20has%20%26quot%3Blost%20his%20mind%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUddhav%20Thackeray%20has%20become%20'bhramishta'%20(delirious).%20He%20is%20hallucinating.%20Initially%2C%20he%20said%20Amit%20Shah%20promised%20him%20a%20chief%20ministership%20in%20some%20room.%20Now%20he%20says%20I%20promised%20to%20make%20his%20son%20a%20CM.%20To%20hide%20one%20falsehood%2C%20another%20lie%20is%20being%20told%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%2C%20however%2C%20admitted%20to%20having%20told%20Mr%20Thackeray%20that%20Aaditya%20should%20be%20trained%20as%20he%20will%20eventually%20take%20control%20of%20the%20party%20(Shiv%20Sena)%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeave%20alone%20making%20him%20(Aaditya)%20a%20chief%20minister%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20make%20him%20even%20a%20minister.%20He%20(Aaditya)%20became%20a%20minister%20later%20(when%20MVA%20was%20in%20power)%20which%20landed%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20in%20its%20current%20situation%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20speech%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20slammed%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20for%20his%20reference%20to%20%26quot%3Bsome%20room%26quot%3B%20during%20his%20talks%20with%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20said%20the%20room%20of%20Bal%20Thackeray%20is%20like%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20late%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray%20because%20he%20was%20always%20true%20to%20his%20word%20and%20never%20deviated%20from%20his%20ideals.%20We%20don't%20respect%20those%20who%20sacrificed%20the%20ideals%20of%20the%20late%20leader%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWho%20are%20you%20trying%20to%20fool%20by%20speaking%20imagined%20scripts%3F%20You%20are%20misleading%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated%20while%20slamming%20Mr%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20further%20said%20that%20Maharashtra's%20%26quot%3Bsocio-politics%26quot%3B%20and%20development%20is%20not%20a%20%26quot%3BSalim-Javed%26quot%3B%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20politics%20and%20development.%20So%20don't%20try%20to%20get%20involved%20in%20such%20scripts.%20You%20will%20get%20a%20befitting%20reply%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20deprecating%20the%20senior%20Thackeray.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20there%20is%20a%20limit%20to%20speaking%20lies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20(Uddhav)%20wanted%20to%20become%20chief%20minister.%20As%20he%20couldn't%20become%20a%20CM%20when%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP%20alliance%2C%20he%20switched%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shinde%20told%20reporters%2C%20referring%20to%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20(undivided)%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20NCP%20(undivided)%20and%20the%20Congress%20post%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20a%20split%20engineered%20by%20Mr%20Shinde%20led%20to%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20Thackeray-led%20MVA%20government%20in%20June%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndica