l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fpeople%2Fkeeping-him-in-jail-like-conviction-before-trial-rana-kapoor-gets-bail-124042000770_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Intense%20Heatwave%20Grips%20Parts%20Of%20India%20As%20Temperatures%20Cross%2040%20Degrees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20searing%20heatwave%20gripped%20parts%20of%20India%20on%20Saturday%2C%20with%20maximum%20temperatures%20ranging%20from%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20to%2046%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20many%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%2C%20heatwave%20to%20severe%20heatwave%20conditions%20prevailed%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Odisha%2C%20and%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%20during%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20ongoing%20heatwave%20affecting%20parts%20of%20Odisha%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20and%20Gangetic%20West%20Bengal%20is%20the%20second%20heatwave%20spell%20this%20month.%20The%20first%20spell%20scorched%20parts%20of%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20maximum%20temperatures%20at%20some%20places%20were%20recorded%20seven%20to%20eight%20degrees%20above%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaripada%20and%20Boudh%20in%20Odisha%20recorded%20a%20maximum%20temperature%20of%2045.2%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20Midnapore%20and%20Bankura%20in%20West%20Bengal%20recorded%2044.5%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%2044.6%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20respectively.%20Daltonganj%20and%20Jamshedpur%20in%20Jharkhand%20registered%2043.6%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%2043.5%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20respectively%2C%20while%20Rajnandgaon%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20reported%2043%20degrees%20Celsius.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heatwave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%20A%20severe%20heatwave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20temperature%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20prevailing%20but%20weakening%20El%20Nino%20conditions%2C%20the%20IMD%20had%20earlier%20warned%20of%20extreme%20heat%20during%20the%20April-June%20period%20when%20around%20a%20billion%20people%20are%20expected%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20during%20the%20seven-phase%20general%20elections%2C%20heightening%20concerns%20about%20vulnerability%20to%20heatwaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20for%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20elections%20took%20place%20on%20Friday%20(April%2019).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Met%20office%20said%20four%20to%20eight%20heatwave%20days%20are%20expected%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20April%20against%20the%20normal%20of%20one%20to%20three%20days.%20Ten%20to%2020%20days%20of%20heatwave%20are%20expected%20against%20the%20normal%20of%20four%20to%20eight%20days%20in%20the%20entire%20April-June%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20areas%20predicted%20to%20see%20more%20heatwave%20days%20are%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20Madhya%20Maharashtra%2C%20Vidarbha%2C%20Marathwada%2C%20Bihar%2C%20and%20Jharkhand.%20Some%20places%20may%20record%20over%2020%20days%20of%20heatwave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intense%20heat%20could%20strain%20power%20grids%20and%20result%20in%20water%20shortages%20in%20parts%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGlobal%20weather%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20IMD%2C%20are%20also%20expecting%20La%20Nina%20conditions%20to%20develop%20later%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEl%20Nino%20conditions%20--%20periodic%20warming%20of%20surface%20waters%20in%20the%20central%20Pacific%20Ocean%20--%20are%20associated%20with%20weaker%20monsoon%20winds%20and%20drier%20conditions%20in%20India.%20La%20Nina%20conditions%20--%20the%20ant