EMr%20Khan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20PTI%2C%20is%20facing%20more%20than%20100%20cases%20and%20has%20been%20lodged%20at%20the%20Adiala%20Jail%20in%20Rawalpindi%20for%20over%20eight%20months%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20abduction%20of%20Imran%20Khan's%20nephew%20Hassan%20Niazi%20and%20another%20young%20PTI%20leader%20Ibad%20Farooq%20from%20military%20captivity.%20We%20want%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20ensure%20their%20immediate%20release%20and%20hold%20kidnappers%20accountable%2C%26quot%3B%20PTI%20spokesperson%20Raoof%20Hasan%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokesperson%20voiced%20great%20concerns%20over%20the%20shifting%20of%20both%20PTI%20leaders%20Hassan%20to%20an%20unknown%20place%20and%20said%20that%20around%20100%20innocent%20citizens%20have%20been%20kept%20in%20illegal%20military%20custody%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BMay%209%20false%20flag%20operation%26quot%3B%2C%20who%20were%20being%20subjected%20to%20political%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inhuman%20treatment%20being%20meted%20out%20with%20the%20young%20PTI%20leaders%20is%20purely%20political%20because%20they%20have%20been%20facing%20the%20worst%20state%20oppression%20and%20brutality%20courageously%20for%20the%20last%2010%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20abduction%20of%20Niazi%20and%20Farooq%20was%20an%20open%20attack%20on%20the%20sanctity%20of%20law%20and%20justice%20and%20a%20violation%20of%20basic%20human%20and%20constitutional%20rights.%20%26quot%3BThe%20trial%20of%20civilians%20under%20military%20laws%20is%20unconstitutional.%26quot%3B%20The%20spokesperson%20further%20said%20it%20is%20shameful%20and%20condemnable%20to%20target%20Mr%20Khan's%20nephew%20Hassan%20Niazi%20as%20political%20revenge%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20unlawfully%20incarcerated%20PTI%20founding%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20coercive%20and%20shameful%20t