f%20Kejriwal%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Tihar%20jail%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Atishi%20said%20the%20report%20has%20%26quot%3Bexposed%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP's%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20is%20underway%20to%20kill%20Kejriwal%20in%20jail.%20The%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20taking%20insulin%20for%2012%20years%2C%20what%20is%20the%20problem%20for%20the%20Tihar%20administration%20to%20give%20insulin%20to%20him%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20minister%20also%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20used%20to%20take%2050%20units%20of%20insulin%20daily%20before%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20--%20who%20is%20under%20the%20care%20of%20a%20Telangana-based%20private%20doctor%20for%20diabetes%20--%20stopped%20taking%20insulin%20a%20few%20months%20ago%20and%2C%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20arrest%2C%20he%20was%20on%20a%20basic%20anti-diabetes%20oral%20tablet%20called%20Metformin%2C%20the%20officials%20said%2C%20citing%20the%20Tihar%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20medical%20check-ups%20in%20Tihar%20jail%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20told%20doctors%20that%20he%20was%20taking%20insulin%20%26quot%3Bsince%20the%20last%20few%20years%20and%20stopped%20taking%20it%20a%20few%20months%20back%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKejriwal's%20alleged%20treatment%20at%20a%20private%20clinic%20in%20Telangana%20is%20a%20curious%20case%20where%20Delhi's%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20who%20boasts%20of%20a%20world-class%20health%20infrastructure%20in%20Delhi%20is%20surreptitiously%20getting%20treated%20at%20a%20south%20India%20clinic%20of%20which%20he%20even%20fails%20to%20provide%20medical%20documents%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNotably%2C%20the%20entry%20of%20this%20Telangana%20clinic%20in%20the%20whole%20episode%20surrounding%20Kejriwal's%20arrest%20in%20the%20excise%20scam%20comes%20close%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20south%20Indian%20liquor%20cartel%20that%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20framing%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20now-scrapped%20excise%20policy%20of%20the%20AAP%20Government%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fd3dbnlq4_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAP%20Condemns%20LG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20in%20a%20statement%20condemned%20the%20Lt%20Governor%20for%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3Bcruel%20and%20inhuman%26quot%3B%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20well-known%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20sugar%20levels%20have%20increased%20to%20alarming%20levels%20and%20crossed%20300%20on%20several%20days%20since%2012th%20April%202024.%20However%2C%20despite%20his%20repeated%20requests%2C%20he%20is%20being%20denied%20insulin%20administration%20by%20Tihar%20Jail%20authorities.%20Not%20a%20single%20doctor%20in%20India%20or%20anywhere%20in%20the%20world%20would%20agree%20that%20a%20severe%20diabetes%20patient%2C%20who%20has%20been%20on%20insulin%20for%20past%2012%20years%2C%20and%20whose%20sugar%20levels%20are%20above%20300%20consistently%20should%20be%20denied%20insulin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYet%2C%20the%20LG%20and%20the%20Tihar%20Jail%20authorities%20have%20decided%20to%20deny%20insulin%20to%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20This%20is%20cruel%2C%20inhuman%20and%20tantamount%20to%20attempt%20to%20murder%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20while%20in%20judicial%20custody%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2021%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20mon