20to%20the%20group%2C%20the%20strong%20scent%20of%20the%20Africa%20(Lynx%20Africa)%20variety%20masks%20the%20hormones%20that%20trigger%20aggression%20in%20rams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20using%20the%20deodorant%2C%20Bryce%20reports%20a%20peaceful%20coexistence%20among%20her%20rams.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20argy-bargy%2C%20no%20rowing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Flifestyle%2Faxe-deodorant-spray-sheep-rams-fighting-9283eaad%3Fst%3D9ycy7rzkve8pffo%26reflink%3Ddesktopwebshare_permalink%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20puff%20themselves%20up%20and%20square%20up%20to%20each%20other%20and%20make%20this%20grunting%20noise%2C%26quot%3B%20explains%20Bryce%2C%2055%20years%20old%2C%20who%20often%20favours%20unwieldy%20Wellington%20boots%20paired%20with%20purple%20nail%20polish%20and%20sparkly%20eye%20shadow.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20when%20you%20see%20drunk%20men%20put%20their%20fists%20up%20and%20say%2C%20'I'll%20fight%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApparently%2C%20this%20fragrant%20solution%20is%20gaining%20traction.%20Bryce%20says%20several%20farmers%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20possibly%20even%20worldwide%2C%20are%20adopting%20this%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20benefits%20extend%20beyond%20preventing%20ram%20fights.%20Ewes%20identify%20their%20young%20by%20smell%2C%20and%20the%20deodorant's%20strong%20scent%20apparently%20tricks%20them%20into%20thinking%20the%20lamb%20belongs%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20go%20for%20Lynx%20Africa%20because%20it%20has%20a%20very%20distinctive%2C%20strong%20smell%2C%26quot%3B%20Caitlin%20Jenkins%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20shepherdess%20in%20nearby%20Suffolk%2C%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20ones%20that%20don't%20smell%20as%20strong%20have%20less%20chance%20of%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxe%20was%20first%20launched%20by%20Unilever%20in%20France%20in%201983%20after%20the%20company%20saw%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market%20for%20a%20strong%20deodorant%20that%20smelled%20like%20cologne.%20The%20brand%20was%20sold%20as%20Lynx%20in%20markets%20where%20the%20Axe%20trademark%20was%20already%20taken%2C%20including%20the%20UK%2C%20Ireland%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713621660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fgotik0ag_lambrams_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Faxe-effect-british-farmers-spray-rams-with-deodorant-to-prevent-fights-5485373%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inspired%20by%20a%20tip%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BLadies%20Who%20Lamb%26quot%3B%20Facebook%20group%2C%20farmers%20like%20Sam%20Bryce%20have%20observed%20a%20decrease%20in%20aggression%20among%20their%20rams%20after%20using%20the%20strong%20scent%20of%20Lynx%20Africa.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Faxe-effect-british-farmers-spray-rams-with-deodorant-to-prevent-fights-5485373%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Faxe-effect-british-farmers-spray-rams-with-deodorant-to-prevent-fights-5485373%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Faxe-effect-british-farmers-spray-rams-with-deodorant-to-prevent-fights-5485373%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Priyanka%20Chopra%20drops%20photos%20from%20Swiss%20Alps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713620890000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109461639%2Cimgsize-76924.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-drops-dreamy-photos-and-videos-from-swiss-alps-can-i-please-stay-see-post%2Farticleshow%2F109461639.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22h