%20matter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsoni-razdan-takes-a-sly-dig-at-mukesh-khannas-strong-criticism-against-zeenat-amans-views-on-live-in-relationships%2Farticleshow%2F109460998.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Poll%20Surveys%20Telecast%20On%20TV%20Are%20%26quot%3BBJP%20Inspired%26quot%3B%2C%20Claims%20Mamata%20Banerjee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20on%20Saturday%20alleged%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20chalked%20out%20seven-phase%20polls%20to%20enable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20to%20carry%20out%20extensive%20campaigning%20using%20the%20nation's%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20at%20Gajol%20in%20Malda%20district%20in%20support%20of%20Maldaha%20Uttar%20TMC%20candidate%20Prasun%20Banerjee%2C%20a%20former%20IPS%20officer%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20the%20party%20supremo%2C%20said%20polls%20have%20been%20scheduled%20from%20April%2019%20to%20June%201%20so%20that%20Modi%20and%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20can%20travel%20on%20special%20planes%20across%20the%20country%20before%20every%20phase%20to%20%26quot%3Boverwhelm%20the%20Opposition%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20earlier%20occasions%2C%20elections%20used%20to%20be%20over%20by%20May%20but%20this%20year%2C%20it%20has%20been%20extended%20till%20June%201%20to%20enable%20Modi%20to%20visit%20various%20places%20on%20military%20planes%2C%20while%20we%20are%20made%20to%20arrange%20for%20our%20own%20transport%2C%20including%20helicopters%2C%20which%20are%20also%20being%20booked%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20so%20that%20we%20get%20little%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20greatly%20inconvenienced%20by%20the%20scorching%20heat%20but%20Modi%20is%20unperturbed%20as%20they%20(BJP%20leaders)%20are%20campaigning%20in%20VVIP%20comfort%20with%20all%20facilities%20at%20hand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20though%20the%20Union%20council%20of%20ministers%20led%20by%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20a%20caretaker%20cabinet%20after%20the%20announcement%20of%20elections%20and%20the%20EC%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20running%20the%20administrative%20machinery%2C%20the%20poll%20body%20is%20%26quot%3Btoeing%20the%20line%20dictated%20by%20Modi%20and%20his%20party%20colleagues%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20BJP%20and%20Congress%20MPs%20from%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20alleged%20that%20despite%20being%20elected%20from%20the%20state%20in%202019%2C%20none%20of%20them%20took%20up%20the%20state's%20cause%20regarding%20the%20release%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds%20by%20the%20Centre%20or%20building%20houses%20for%20the%20poor%20under%20PM%20Awas%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20our%20(TMC)%20MPs%20were%20manhandled%20and%20arrested%20when%20they%20went%20to%20Delhi%20in%20November%20last%20year%20to%20demand%20the%20release%20of%20MGNREGA%20funds%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20have%20the%20Congress%20and%20BJP%20MPs%20done%20for%20the%20poor%3F%20What%20has%20(Maldaha%20Uttar)%20BJP%20MP%20Khagen%20Murmu%20done%20for%20job%20card%20holders%20of%20the%20state%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20CPI%20(M)%20and%20Congress%20of%20bolstering%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20and%20urged%20people%20not%20to%20cast%20votes%20for%20any%20non-TMC%20candidate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20coined%20the%20name%20of%20INDIA%20bloc.%20But%20INDIA%20bloc%20does%20not%20exist%20in%20Bengal.%20For%20us%2C%20it%20exists%20outside%20the%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20was%20expelled%20from%20Parliament%20for%20unmasking%20the%20misdeeds%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20and%20its%20proximity%20to%20big%20business%20houses.%20TMC%20MPs%20were%20targeted%20by%20this%20vindictive%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20TMC%20MPs%2C%20including%20Mamata%20Bala%20Thakur%20and%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20were%20sent%20back%20from%20Guwahati%20airport%20when%20they%20went%20to%20Assam%20after%20the%20names%20of%2019%20lakh%20Bengalis%20were%20left%20out%20of%20NRC%2C%20Banerjee%20asserted%20that%20her%20party%20has%20always%20stood%20up%20to%20%26quot%3Batrocities%20committed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20churches%2C%20mosques%20and%20other%20places%20of%20worship%20were%20vandalised%20in%20Manipur%20during%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20and%20the%20BJP%20governments%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20Centre%20looked%20the%20other%20way%2C%20it%20was%20the%20TMC%20that%20stood%20by%20the%20affected%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20destroy%20places%20of%20worship%20while%20we%20build%20those.%20The%20BJP%20boasts%20about%20Ram%20temple%2C%20but%20how%20many%20temples%20have%20they%20actually%20built%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years%3F%20It%20is%20the%20TMC%20that%20has%20built%20Durga%2C%20Kali%20and%20Jagannath%20temples%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20conspiring%20to%20engineer%20riots%20by%20spreading%20fake%20news%20and%20videos%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20claimed%20that%20poll%20surveys%20telecast%20on%20TV%20channels%20were%20%26quot%3BBJP%20inspired%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20asserted%20that%20the%20TMC%20will%20get%20a%20huge%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20the%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20public%20rally%20in%20Manichak%20in%20Maldaha%20Dakshin%20constituency%20in%20support%20of%20TMC%20candidate%20Shahnawaz%20Ali%20Raihan%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20flagged%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%2C%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20is%20%26quot%3Bplotting%20to%20impose%20UCC%20by%20taking%20away%20people's%20individual%20rights%20and%20liberty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20oppose%20UCC%20imposition%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20BJP's%20target%20of%20winning%20over%20400%20seats%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20will%20not%20win%20even%20200%20seats.%20In%20most%20states%20in%20the%20south%20and%20north%2C%20they%20will%20fare%20miserably.%26quot%3B%20A%20party%20cannot%20win%20polls%20just%20by%20depending%20on%20central%20forces%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20afraid%20of%20CBI%2C%20ED%20and%20NIA.%20However%20hard%20the%20BJP%20tries%20to%20use%20these%20agencies%2C%20it%20will%20not%20come%20back%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713618120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhob51vgo_mamata-banerjee-1200-_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-chalked-out-7-phase-polls-to-assist-bjp-campaign-claims-mamata-banerjee-5484241%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20on%20Saturday%20alleged%20that%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20chalked%20out%20seven-phase%20polls%20to%20enable%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20his%20cabinet%20colleagues%20to%20carry%20out%20extensive%20campaigning%20using%20the%20nation's%20resources.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-chalked-out-7-phase-polls-to-assist-bjp-campaign-claims-mamata-baner