%20in%20Germany%20and%20Dalton%20Maag%20in%20the%20UK%20were%20pivotal%20in%20preparing%20him%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20venture.%20They%20taught%20him%20the%20crucial%20blend%20of%20precision%20and%20creativity%20needed%20in%20type%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20single%20day%20not%20thinking%20about%20fonts.%20A%20font%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20letters%2C%20numbers%20and%20symbols%2C%20all%20dressed%20up%20in%20a%20certain%20style.%20When%20I%20design%20fonts%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20designing%20outfits%20for%20words%20so%20they%20can%20express%20different%20emotions%20and%20ideas%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFonts%20have%20long-term%20value.%20For%20instance%2C%20Helvetica%20was%20first%20published%20in%201957%2C%20yet%20this%20font%20remains%20relevant%20even%20today.%20ITF%20develops%20both%20traditional%20fonts%20(used%20for%20text%20in%20books%20and%20newspapers)%20and%20experimental%20or%20display%20fonts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20fonts%2C%20such%20as%20Times%20New%20Roman%20and%20Arial%2C%20prioritise%20readability%20and%20versatility.%20In%20contrast%2C%20experimental%20fonts%20go%20beyond%20functionality%20and%20embrace%20innovative%20shapes%2C%20concepts%20and%20designs.%20These%20fonts%20prioritise%20artistic%20expression%20and%20invigorate%20visual%20design.%20They%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20character%20and%20are%20used%20in%20headlines%2C%20logos%20and%20posters.%20For%20sports%20events%2C%20children%E2%80%99s%20books%2C%20and%20film%20posters%2C%20%E2%80%98grunge%E2%80%99%20(messy%20text)%20is%20used%20at%20times%2C%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Satya%20making%20a%20presentation%20about%20the%20various%20Indian%20language%20fonts%20by%20ITF.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FMaking-a-presentation_11zon-1713536103-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347883%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESatya%20making%20a%20presentation%20about%20the%20various%20Indian%20language%20fonts%20by%20ITF.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%E2%80%99s%20most%20popular%20font%20is%20the%20Kohinoor%20series%20designed%20by%20Satya.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20Kohinoor%2C%20there%20was%20no%20font%20that%20could%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246205%2F83-yo-kerala-school-dropout-creates-unique-dictionary-in-4-south-indian-languages-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupport%20all%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20instance%2C%20in%20an%20airport%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20we%20need%20signage%20in%20three%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20English%2C%20Hindi%2C%20and%20Gujarati.%20Fonts%20in%20a%20family%20are%20aesthetically%20consistent.%20Apple%20has%20licensed%20the%20Kohinoor%20family.%20If%20you%20get%20a%20message%20in%20Hindi%20or%20Gujarati%20from%20an%20Apple%20device%2C%20the%20font%20will%20be%20from%20our%20Kohinoor%20series%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20Kohinoor%20font%20