te%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CApplying%20the%20hierarchy%20of%20needs%20principle%2C%20I%20cannot%20bring%20myself%20to%20use%20clear%20RO%20waste%20water%20on%20plants%2C%20as%20cloudy%20water%20collected%20from%20washing%20vegetables%2Fdals%20works%20perfectly%20here%20or%20for%20rinsing%20dirty%20dishes%20%E2%80%93%20again%20why%20use%20water%20of%20a%20higher%20purity%20than%20needed!%20I%20use%20the%20rejected%20water%20from%20the%20RO%20for%20mopping%20and%20then%20reuse%20it%20again%20for%20watering%20plants%2C%20possibly%20because%20I%20use%20organic%20cleaners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Odette%20makes%20organic%20cleaners%20that%20make%20the%20water%20safe%20to%20reuse.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20place%20of%20toilet%20cleaners%20and%20floor%20cleaners%2C%20I%20use%20homemade%20bio%20enzymes%20that%20can%20be%20used%20to%20clean%20bathrooms%2C%20floors%2C%20and%20disinfect%20fruits.%20I%20reuse%20this%20to%20water%20my%20plants.%20Bio%20enzymes%20are%20beneficial%20for%20plants%20as%20it%20acts%20as%20a%20fertiliser%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-1-1713426011.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Odette%20claims%20to%20use%20around%201500%20litres%20less%20water%20per%20day%20than%20an%20equivalent%20household.%C2%A0%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-1-1713426011.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-1-1713426011-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FOdette-1-1713426011-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetter