k%20a%20toll%20on%20his%20MMA%20career.%20And%20that%20realisation%20dawned%20on%20him%20after%20his%20first%20professional%20loss%20in%20December%202021%20to%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Angad%20Bisht%20at%20MFN-7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20I%20took%20this%20fight%20on%20short%20notice%20without%20a%20training%20camp.%20All%20I%20did%20before%20this%20fight%20was%20run%2C%20sweat%20and%20make%20weight.%20I%20took%20this%20fight%20because%20I%20needed%20the%20money%20to%20pay%20back%20interest%20on%20a%20loan%20my%20family%20had%20taken.%20After%20losing%20the%20fight%2C%20however%2C%20I%20contemplated%20suicide.%20My%20wrestling%20career%20fell%20apart%20before%20it%20could%20start%20and%20I%20had%20just%20suffered%20my%20first%20loss%20in%20MMA.%20Losing%20this%20fight%20really%20forced%20me%20to%20introspect.%20While%20Roshan%20was%20training%20in%20Singapore%2C%20there%20was%20no%20one%20I%20could%20train%20with%20in%20Manipur%20who%20could%20take%20my%20game%20to%20the%20next%20level.%20So%2C%20I%20conveyed%20this%20message%20to%20Roshan%20and%20said%20I%20needed%20to%20train%20outside%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chungreng%20Koren%20competing%20at%20an%20MFN%20event%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungreng-ground-and-pound-1713276782-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FChungren